The paper focuses on image translation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves regularization during training, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The use of an auxiliary domain and multi-path consistency loss also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves image processing, which falls under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
